Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>1. Í íTIKAI kūinira Jehova rüimbo rüerū!
műinire Jehova, inyui andū othe a thi.</s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Inirai Jehova, gathai ritwa rīake;
hunjagiai ühoro wa ühonokania wake müthenya o mūthenya.</s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>Icokia: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>lgùrù ta nì gùkene, thì nayo nì icanjamüke</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>2. Igürű ta nirikene, thĩ nayo nīicanjamüke;
iria riria inene nirirurume, gwata kiria giothe kiriiyūire;</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Werū-ini nakuo nigükenűrürüke, gwata indo ciothe iria ii kuo;</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>hindi io mití yothe ya mütitü no yuge ngemi;</s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>Icokia: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>lgùrù ta nì gùkene, thì nayo nì icanjamüke</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>3.Nigwikwo üguo mbere-ini ya Jehova, tondũ niegūüka;
gūüka nīegūüka güthamaka th</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>:</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>arithamakaga mabūũrüri na űthingu,
atuithanagie irindi na wihokeku wake.</s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846><kFFFF0000>Icokia: </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>lgùrù ta nì gùkene, thì nayo nì icanjamüke</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Rùimbo rwa Injili:</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluia, alleluia.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Muthenya mwamùre nì utwariire.</s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Inyui mabùrùri ùkai mùgooce,
Mwathani tondū ùmùthi ūtheri mùnene nì wariire thi.</s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>Alleluia.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>INJILI: 
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFFF0000>(John 1: 1-18)</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>O KİAMBÍRİRIA-RĨ, Ühoro wari o kuo, naguo </s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Uhoro watûire o hari Ngai, o naguo Uhoro wari o Ngai.</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Ucio, Uhoro-ri, niaagitüire hari
Ngai o kiambiriria.</s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Indo ciothe ikigia ciagiire na ündū wake, </s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>na kindú o gīothe kiria kigiite, gūtirī kiagiire we atari ho, o na kimwe. </s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Thíiní wake nikuo kwari muoyo,. naguo muoyo ücio niguo wari ütheri wa andū.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Naguo ūtheri niūtüire o ütherete nduma-ini, nayo nduma ndiaühootire.</s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Nigwokire mùndiũ wareketio ni Ngai, wetagwo Johana. </s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Mündú ücio okire ni ündů wa üira, oimbūre ühoro wa ûtheri ücio, </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>ni getha andü othe metíkie ni ûndü wake.</s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Na tiwe ütheri ûcio; okire no getha oimbūre ühoro waguo, ûtheri ücio.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Utheri kūna, ũria ümūrikagira mündũ o wothe, niĩwari kuo ügīükaga thi. </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>We, Utheri ücio, aari güků thi, o nayo th</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> īkigia yagīire na ündū wake, </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>nakio k</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846>rindi gia gūkū th</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> gikiaga kūmümenya. </s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Okire gwake mwene, nao andū ake mwene matiigana kümwitikira.</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>No aria othe maanwitikirire, nio aria mehokete riitwa riake, </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>acio akimahotithia gütuika ciana cia Ngai,  itaaciarirūo ni thakame, </s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>kana igīciarūo ni kwenda kwa mwiri kana kwenda kwa mündů, no Ngai. </s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>We, Ühoro-ri, agīgituika mũndů, agitüürania na ithu aiyüirūo n</s></f><fSegoe UI Black><s1846>ỉ</s></f><fArial Black><s1846> ûtugi na ühoro-ûria-wa-ma, </s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>na ithui tůkiionera riri wake, riri o ta wa mwana wa mũmwe oimite kūri Ithe.</s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Johana nioimbūrite ühoro wake, akaanirira akoiga atiri, </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Ucio nowe ndoigire, ati, Uria ügūûka thutha wakwa niagīite mbere yakwa, </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>nī gūkorūo aari kuo mbere yakwa. Amu-rī, thiini wa kūiyürūo </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kūu gwake twanaheo ithuothe, tügitugagwo ringi na ringi.  </s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Tondü watho watümirūo na
Musa; ütugi na îhoro-ûria-wa-ma mokire na Jesu Kristo. </s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Gūtiri mündü üri ona Ngai; Müriũ wa mūmwe, ûrīa wi githūri-ini gia Ithe, niwe uumbūrite ihoro wake.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<s1846></s><fArial Black><s1846>Ino niyo Injili ya Mwathani.</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,Style:{Background:{Image:"OIP (3).jpg",Luminosity:-50}},
Text:"MWAKA MWERU MITHA YA UTUKU"},{Guid:"InJ77GyF7UaD4S14e699nw",Verses:[{
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFD80000>SOMO LA KWANZA
</k></s></f><u><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>1 Yohane 2:18-21</k></c></s></f></u>"},{ID:2,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Somo katika barua ya kwanza ya Mtakatifu Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:3,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Watoto, ni wakati wa mwisho.
Ni kama mlivyosikia, mpinga Kristo hana budi kuja.</s></f>"},{ID:4,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sasa wapinga Kristo wengi wamekwishafika.
Hivyo tumetambua ya kuwa ni wakati wa mwisho.</s></f>"},{ID:5,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Wametokea kwetu, lakini si wenzetu.
Kama wangalikuwa wenzetu,
wangalishinda kwetu.</s></f>"},{ID:6,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini wametokea,
kusudi waonekane wazi
ya kuwa hakuna hata mmoja wao ambaye ni mwenzetu.</s></f>"},{ID:7,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini ninyi mmepakwa mafuta na yeye aliye Mtakatifu,
na nyote mmejaliwa ujuzi.</s></f>"},{ID:8,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Sikuwaandikieni kama watu wasioijua kweli,
bali kama watu waijuao, kwa sababu kweli haizai uongo wowote.</s></f>"},{ID:9,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno la Bwana.</s></f>"},{ID:10,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ZABURI YA KUITIKIZANA
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Zaburi 96:1-2, 11-12, 13 (K. 1la)</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:11,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFD80000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Mbingu na zifurahi, nchi na ishangilie.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:12,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwimbieni Bwana wimbo mpya;
mwimbieni Bwana, nchi yote.</s></f>"},{ID:13,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwimbieni Bwana, lisifuni jina lake;
siku kwa siku tangazeni wokovu wake. K.</s></f>"},{ID:14,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFD80000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Mbingu na zifurahi, nchi na ishangilie.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:15,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mbingu na zifurahi, nchi na ishangilie;
bahari na ivume na vyote viljazavyo;</s></f>"},{ID:16,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>mashamba na yachangamke, na vyote vilivyomo. K.</s></f>"},{ID:17,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFD80000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Mbingu na zifurahi, nchi na ishangilie.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:18,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndipo miti yote ya msituni itaimba kwa furaha,
mbele za Bwana, kwa kuwa anakuja,</s></f>"},{ID:19,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>kwa kuwa anakuja kuihukumu nchi;
atauhukumu ulimwengu kwa haki,</s></f>"},{ID:20,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>nayo mataifa kwa uaminifu wake. K.</s></f>"},{ID:21,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><kFFD80000>K. </k></s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Mbingu na zifurahi, nchi na ishangilie.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:22,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>SHANGILIO LA INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Yohane 1:14a, 12a</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:23,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>K. Aleluya.
W. Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:24,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>K. Neno alifanyika mwili, akakaa kwetu.
Wote waliompokea</s></f>"},{ID:25,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>aliwapa uwezo wa kuwa watoto wa Mungu</s></f>"},{ID:26,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>W. Aleluya.</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:27,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>INJILI
</s></f><fArial Black><s1846><cFFF2F200><kFFD80000>Yohane 11:1-18</k></c></s></f>"},{ID:28,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwanzo wa Injili takatifu ilivyoandikwa na Yohane</s></f>"},{ID:29,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Mwanzoni kulikuwako Neno, naye Neno alikuwa kwa Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:30,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Na Neno huyu alikuwa Mungu.
Huyu mwanzoni alikuwako kwa Mungu. </s></f>"},{ID:31,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa Neno vyote vimeumbwa, na pasipo Neno hakikuumbwa chochote kilichoumbwa.</s></f>"},{ID:32,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Ndani yake ulikuwamo uzima, na uzima ulikuwa ni mwanga wa wanadamu; </s></f>"},{ID:33,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>na mwanga huo uliangaza gizani, lakini giza
halikuupokea. </s></f>"},{ID:34,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Palitokea mtu, ametumwa na Mungu, jina lake
Yohane.</s></f>"},{ID:35,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Huyo alikuja kutoa ushuhuda, apate kuushuhudia mwanga ili wasadiki kwa sababu yake. </s></f>"},{ID:36,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yeye hakuwa ule mwanga, ila wajibu
wake ulikuwa kuushuhudia ule mwanga. </s></f>"},{ID:37,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alikuwako mwanga
halisi amwangazaye kila mtu, alikuwa ulimwenguni humu.</s></f>"},{ID:38,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Alikuwako ulimwenguni, nao ulimwengu uliumbwa kwa njia yake,</s></f>"},{ID:39,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>lakini ulimwengu haukumtambua.
Alifika kwa walio wake, nao walio wake hawakumpokea. </s></f>"},{ID:40,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Lakini wote waliompokea aliwapa uwezo wa kuwa watoto wa Mungu,</s></f>"},{ID:41,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>ndio wale wasadikio kwa jina lake, waliozaliwa, si kwa damu,</s></f>"},{ID:42,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>wala kwa tamaa ya mwili, wala kwa tamaa ya mwanadamu bali kwa mapenzi ya Mungu.</s></f>"},{ID:43,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Neno akafanyika mwili, akakaa kwetu; nasi tumeuona utukufu wake, </s></f>"},{ID:44,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>utukufu kama wa mzaliwa wa pekee wa Baba, amejaa
na kweli. </s></f>"},{ID:45,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Yohane alimshuhudia na alipaza sauti akasema, “Huyu ndiye niliyemtaja niliposema, </s></f>"},{ID:46,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Anayekuja nyuma yangu amekuwa
mbele yangu, kwa maana alikuwa kabla yangu.</s></f>"},{ID:47,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Katika ukamilifu wake sisi sote tumepokea neema juu ya neema.</s></f>"},{ID:48,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Kwa maana sheria imetolewa kwa njia ya Musa, lakini neema na kweli zimepatikana kwa Yesu Kristo.</s></f>"},{ID:49,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Hakuna aliyemwona Mungu. Mwana wa pekee, Mungu, aliyekifuani mwa Baba, amemtambulisha kwetu.</s></f>"},{ID:50,
Text:"<fArial Black><s1846>Injili ya Bwana.</s></f>"}],VideoDuration:0,Style:{Background:{Image:"OIP (3).jpg",Luminosity:-55}},
